  "**Thanks to Weed-Lancer for tons of grammar errors fix**": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "**Weed-Lancerへの感謝：文法誤りの多数修正**",
      "CN": "感谢 Weed-Lancer 修正了大量语法错误",
      "KR": "Weed-Lancer님 덕분에 문법 오류 대다수 수정",
